[[中華人民共和國政府|中華人民共和國政府]]稱為「北平和-{}-平解放」。[[中華民國政府|中華民國政府]]稱為「北平淪-{}-陷」。<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://news.gpwb.gov.tw/Magazine/101030 | title=《第三週研讀》板蕩忠臣，戡亂戰役 | date=2014-11-01 | publisher=中華民國國防部[[青年日報|青年日報]] | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160921021753/http://news.gpwb.gov.tw/Magazine/101030 | archivedate=2016-09-21 | accessdate=2016-09-06 }}</ref>其他名稱包括「北平易帜」<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://dangshi.people.com.cn/GB/8716255.html | title=傅作义的西柏坡之行 | publisher=[[人民网|人民网]] | access-date=2015-03-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402132910/http://dangshi.people.com.cn/GB/8716255.html | archive-date=2015-04-02 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news | url=http://news.ifeng.com/history/1/midang/200901/0123_2664_982271.shtml | title=北平易帜 傅作义亲到西柏坡打探毛泽东底细 | publisher=[[凤凰网|凤凰网]] | access-date=2015-03-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140815211551/http://news.ifeng.com/history/1/midang/200901/0123_2664_982271.shtml | archive-date=2014-08-15 | dead-url=no }}</ref>、「中共和平進佔北平」<ref name="林桶法2003">{{cite book|author=林桶法|title=戰後中國的變局 以國民黨為中心的探討|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=9t6MlLP6TDgC&pg=PT199|year=2003|publisher=臺灣商務印書館|isbn=978-957-05-1821-4|pages=199–|access-date=2015-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150320174144/http://books.google.com/books?id=9t6MlLP6TDgC&pg=PT199|archive-date=2015-03-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>、「進佔北平的接與管」<ref name="中國的關键年代學術討論會編輯委員會2000">{{cite book|author=一九四九年 :中國的關键年代學術討論會編輯委員會|title=一九四九年 中國的關键年代學術討論會論文集|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=BoxdAAAAIAAJ|year=2000|publisher=國史館|isbn=978-957-02-7244-4|access-date=2015-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150320194327/http://books.google.com/books?id=BoxdAAAAIAAJ|archive-date=2015-03-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>、「共軍和平進佔北平」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.slc.edu.hk/CustomPage/47/content/chinese_hist_doc/chist/6-6HIST.DOC |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402105355/http://www.slc.edu.hk/Cust